      "options": {
        "content": "### \u2139\ufe0f About This Report\nCard lifecycle events from FIS STDNONMON Data XTRACT v3.0. One row per event per card \u2014 enrollment, status changes, activation, closure. Click any tile to jump to the detail table.\n\n| Column | Source | Meaning |\n|---|---|---|\n| Event Type Code | `fact_non_monetary.event_type_code` | FIS event classification. 1530=New Account \u00b7 1250=Card Ordered \u00b7 4=Insurance/Medicaid |\n| Event Description | `fact_non_monetary.event_description` | Human-readable event text from FIS |\n| Event Datetime | `fact_non_monetary.event_datetime` | When the event occurred at FIS |\n| Card Status Code | `fact_non_monetary.card_status_code` | 1=Active \u00b7 2=Suspended \u00b7 3=Closed |\n| Event Source | `fact_non_monetary.event_source` | Who/what triggered the event (Self, ClientWebUser, etc.) |\n| Person ID | `fact_non_monetary.person_id` | FIS person identifier (same as `dim_member.fis_person_id`) |\n| Pan Proxy | `fact_non_monetary.pan_proxy_number` | Card proxy number used by FIS |\n\n> 166 card enrollment events loaded from STDNONMON03312026_RFU.txt.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.4.3"
    },
